      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ECHOES OF DAD (1) was in the placings last time but three back produced a sharp 34.33 win over 595m at this track. Rates on top and can find winning form again. REALITY IS (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 42.94 beating MOSCOW CHICK. Leading chance again. GINNY'S RUN (2) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (34.82) in a OPEN at this track. Can hit the frame this time. ISABELLA'S BLITZ (6) is a course and distance winner worth keeping in mind.",
